$ CSS: A tag can have multiple classes

The following simple → development/web/HTML[HTML] document tries to demonstrate that a
→ development/web/HTML/tags[HTML tag] can have multiple classes associated with it.

gh|about-CSS|/classes/multiple-classes-for-tag.html||

When the document is rendered in a → development/web/browser[browser], it might produce something like
gh|about-CSS|/classes/img/multiple-classes-for-tag.png||
